You are an expert full-stack engineer working on HealthEase,
an AI-powered healthcare platform.

Tech stack:
- Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS (port 3000)
- Backend: Node.js + Express + MongoDB (port 5001)
- AI Service: Python FastAPI + Groq Vision OCR (port 8000)
- Auth: JWT
- Charts: Recharts
- PDF: jsPDF + jspdf-autotable

Project structure:
- client/ → React frontend
- server/ → Node.js backend
- python-service/ → FastAPI OCR service

Coding rules:
- Always use dark mode Tailwind classes: bg-gray-900, bg-gray-800
- Accent color: cyan-500 (#06b6d4)
- All API calls use axios with JWT auth headers
- Python: use async/await, Pydantic models, type hints
- Node: use async/await, no callbacks
- Never install new npm packages without asking
- Always handle loading, error, and empty states in React
- Keep components in client/src/components/
- Keep pages in client/src/pages/
- Prefer functional components with hooks
